Figure 2 shows the onboard avionics system and Figure 3 illustrates the Spoonbill UAV system architecture. The onboard computer acts as the central processing unit. It is a PC/104 embedded computer produced by Advantech Co., Ltd. The onboard computer is operating under a Windows-XP embedded operating system and the flight control computer program is written using

